<h3 id="performance">Performance</h3>

<h4 id="time">Time</h4>
<p>wall-clock time, response time, elapsed time, CPU time</p>

<h5 id="cpu-time">CPU Time</h5>
<p>CPU Time = CPU time spent for a given program
= Cycles/Program (=Clock Cycles) * Seconds/Cycle (=Clock Cycle Time)
= Instructions/Programs (=IC) * Cycles Instruction (=CPI) * Seconds/Cycle</p>

